headline: Listen: How Logistics Operators Are Navigating Trade-War Turmoil
summary: How are the companies delivering the goods you use every day dealing with President Trump’s trade war? Logistics companies such as warehouse operator Prologis, trucking giant J.B. Hunt and parcel carrier United Parcel Service are coping with rapid shifts in freight demand.
